beer.beer_description: For the latest in our Aotearoa series, we have brewed a focused yet lavish Red India Pale Ale. Pouring a deep mahogany hue, this beer balances a rich malt base with a combination of NZ-grown hops picked for their stonefruit, pine, and citrus character. Rich and malty, but also dry and hoppy. Sweet result.
